title: Learning Notes - React Hooks
content:
React Hooks Deep Dive

Understanding the advanced patterns and best practices:

  • useState: Managing component state
  • useEffect: Side effects and lifecycle
  • useContext: Consuming context values
  • useReducer: Complex state management

Custom hooks can encapsulate logic and make components cleaner.

title: Book Summary - Atomic Habits
content:
Atomic Habits by James Clear

Key takeaways from this excellent book on habit formation:

  • Make it obvious - Design your environment
  • Make it attractive - Bundle with enjoyable activities
  • Make it easy - Reduce friction
  • Make it satisfying - Immediate rewards

Small changes compound over time to create remarkable results.
